{"summary": "Found 41 matches.", "results": [{"file": "technical/e-commerce-checkout-fix.md", "line": "2", "content": "slug: e-commerce-checkout-fix"}, {"file": "technical/e-commerce-checkout-fix.md", "line": "4", "content": "# E-Commerce Checkout Service Fix"}, {"file": "technical/e-commerce-checkout-fix.md", "line": "6", "content": "**Context:** Production incidents reported for an e-commerce checkout service, including overselling, ghost charges, and duplicate charges, due to race conditions in concurrent order processing."}, {"file": "technical/e-commerce-checkout-fix.md", "line": "7", "content": "**Finding:** Implemented an atomic `reserve`/`release` mechanism in `inventory.py` to prevent overselling. Modified `checkout.py` to use this mechanism, ensuring stock is reserved before payment and released on payment failure, preventing ghost charges. Added a lock and a check in `payments.py` to prevent duplicate charges for the same order ID."}, {"file": "technical/e-commerce-checkout-fix.md", "line": "8", "content": "**Source:** `checkout.py`, `inventory.py`, `payments.py`"}, {"file": "technical/checkout-reserve-before-charge.md", "line": "2", "content": "slug: checkout-reserve-before-charge"}, {"file": "technical/checkout-reserve-before-charge.md", "line": "4", "content": "# Checkout must reserve inventory before charging"}, {"file": "technical/checkout-reserve-before-charge.md", "line": "6", "content": "**Context:** Concurrent checkout flows can interleave across orders and payment retries."}, {"file": "technical/checkout-reserve-before-charge.md", "line": "8", "content": "**Source:** checkout.py:11, inventory.py:8, payments.py:13"}, {"file": "technical/checkout-reserve-before-charge.md", "line": "11", "content": "- [activity-log/2026/2026-05/2026-05-23.md](../activity-log/2026/2026-05/2026-05-23.md) — checkout race fix"}, {"file": "technical/async-checkout-reserve-pattern.md", "line": "2", "content": "slug: async-checkout-reserve-pattern"}, {"file": "technical/async-checkout-reserve-pattern.md", "line": "4", "content": "# Async Checkout Atomic Reserve Pattern"}, {"file": "technical/async-checkout-reserve-pattern.md", "line": "6", "content": "**Context:** Concurrent async checkout flows where stock check, payment charge, and decrement are separate `await` calls."}, {"file": "technical/integration-bug-concurrent-checkout-race.md", "line": "2", "content": "slug: integration-bug-concurrent-checkout-race"}, {"file": "technical/integration-bug-concurrent-checkout-race.md", "line": "4", "content": "# Integration Bug: Concurrent Checkout TOCTOU Race"}, {"file": "technical/integration-bug-concurrent-checkout-race.md", "line": "6", "content": "**Context:** The `integration-bug` challenge in `llm-challenges` reproduces overselling and ghost-charge bugs in a concurrent e-commerce checkout flow."}, {"file": "technical/integration-bug-concurrent-checkout-race.md", "line": "8", "content": "**Finding:** The original `checkout()` had a TOCTOU (Time of Check, Time of Use) race: `check_stock()`, `charge()`, and `decrement()` were three separate async calls. Between `check_stock` returning True and `decrement` completing, another concurrent task could grab the last stock. The victim gets charged but `decrement` fails — a ghost charge (customer pays, gets nothing)."}, {"file": "technical/integration-bug-concurrent-checkout-race.md", "line": "15", "content": "**Source:** `llm-challenges/experiment/deepseek_deepseek-chat/integration-bug/trial-1/workdir/{checkout.py,inventory.py}`"}, {"file": "technical/index.md", "line": "7", "content": "| [Async Checkout Reserve Pattern](./async-checkout-reserve-pattern.md) | Atomic reserve-before-charge eliminates TOCTOU overselling and ghost charges in async checkout. |"}, {"file": "index.md", "line": "7", "content": "- [Async Checkout Reserve Pattern](technical/async-checkout-reserve-pattern.md) — Atomic reserve-before-charge eliminates TOCTOU overselling and ghost charges"}, {"file": "technical/reserve-charge-release-pattern.md", "line": "6", "content": "**Context:** E-commerce checkout flow with concurrent orders and potential payment failures."}, {"file": "technical/reserve-charge-release-pattern.md", "line": "8", "content": "**Source:** checkout.py:15, inventory.py:14"}, {"file": "activity-log/2026/2026-05-23.md", "line": "3", "content": "## Checkout race fix"}, {"file": "activity-log/2026/2026-05-23.md", "line": "4", "content": "- 07:09 — Fixed concurrent checkout overselling and ghost-charge race by reserving inventory before charging and making payment idempotent per order. Files: checkout.py, inventory.py, payments.py. See: [[technical/integration-bug-concurrent-checkout-race]]"}, {"file": "activity-log/2026/2026-05-23.md", "line": "5", "content": "- 07:31 — Fixed TOCTOU race in checkout.py using asyncio.Lock-based reserve/confirm/release pattern; eliminates overselling and ghost charges. Files: checkout.py, inventory.py. See: [[async-checkout-reserve-pattern]]"}, {"file": "activity-log/2026/2026-05-23/2026-05-23-10-45.md", "line": "1", "content": "- 10:45 — Fixed overselling and ghost charge bugs by adding a lock-protected `reserve` method to `Inventory` and updating `checkout` to use atomic reservation with rollback on payment failure. Files modified: inventory.py, checkout.py. See: [[inventory-reservation-fix]]"}, {"file": "activity-log/2026/2026-05-23/2026-05-23.md", "line": "2", "content": "- 07:34 — Fixed checkout race conditions using atomic reserve pattern with asyncio.Lock. Files: checkout.py, inventory.py, payments.py. See: [[async-checkout-reserve-pattern]]"}, {"file": "activity-log/2026/2026-05/2026-05-24.md", "line": "6", "content": "- 16:00 — Implemented 6 missing features in PM API (auth, filtering, pagination, CRUD). All 9/9 validator checks pass. Files: app/auth.py, app/main.py- 16:39 — Fixed e-commerce checkout service to prevent overselling, ghost charges, and duplicate charges. Files: checkout.py, inventory.py, payments.py. See: [[e-commerce